videos.description: Larry Austin Jr. tosses to Ejike Obinna who takes it to the rim for Vanderbilt in the first half against Seton Hall.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_OnePlay_(Vanderbilt's Austin feeds Obinna for slam dunk) 2017/11/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Austin feeds Obinna for slam dunk

videos.description: Myles Powell makes a nice underneath pass to Michael Nzei who slams it to extend the Pirates lead 46-34 against the Commodores in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Nzei throws it down for Seton Hall) 2017/24/11 ESHEET
